snippet.title: Typing of the Dead: Love at First Bite DLC - Happy Valentine's Day!
snippet.description:
Happy Valentine's Day everyone! I tried to find games that fit the day and all I could come up with was Love at First Bite. Forgive me for my horrible typing and I hope you enjoyed this. I also hope you all had a great day today. Thanks for watching.

+Like if you enjoyed this.
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/19sqXxf
